OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779711071
OL,3,CMan detained in hospital for killing
OL,4,Cmum in 'senseless' attack
OL,6,FA man who stabbed his mother to death
OL,7,Fwill be detained in hospital
OL,8,Findefinitely over what police called a
OL,9,F"tragic and senseless killing".
OL,11,FRick Parker, now 42, stabbed and
OL,12,Fstrangled 59-year-old Helen Harrison
OL,13,Fat their home on Aspen Close, Market
OL,14,FWeighton, East Yorkshire, in March
OL,15,F2023.
OL,17,FHe was initially charged with murder
OL,18,Fbut was then found unfit to plead due
OL,19,Fto mental health issues.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
