FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779711071
OL,3,CMan detained in hospital for killing
OL,4,Cmum in 'senseless' attack
OL,6,FA trial of facts was held in 2024,
OL,7,Fwhen a jury found Parker had carried
OL,8,Fout the killing and he was given a
OL,9,Fhospital order.
OL,11,FIn July of last year he was reassessed
OL,12,Fas being fit to stand trial for murder
OL,13,Fbut, following medical assessments, he
OL,14,Fwas found to have diminished
OL,15,Fresponsibility and pleaded guilty to
OL,16,Fmanslaughter.
OL,18,FHe also pleaded guilty to causing
OL,19,Factual bodily harm to his stepfather
OL,20,Fover a separate incident in February
OL,21,F2023.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
