FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779711071
OL,3,CMan detained in hospital for killing
OL,4,Cmum in 'senseless' attack
OL,6,FOn Friday Parker was given an
OL,7,Findefinite hospital order.
OL,9,FDet Supt Nicola Burnett, of Humberside
OL,10,FPolice, said: "This was a tragic and
OL,11,Fsenseless killing that has left a
OL,12,Ffamily utterly heartbroken by the loss
OL,13,Fof their loved one in truly horrific
OL,14,Fcircumstances.
OL,16,F"They have been through a harrowing
OL,17,Ftribulation, and my thoughts remain
OL,18,Fwith them at this incredibly difficult
OL,19,Ftime."
OL,26,@rD@OOUxD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
