PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1779711071
OL,3,CMan detained in hospital for killing
OL,4,Cmum in 'senseless' attack
OL,6,FHull Crown Court previously heard
OL,7,FParker had developed mental health
OL,8,Fproblems following a road accident.
OL,10,FHe attacked Ms Harrison on 5 March
OL,11,F2023 after she called for an ambulance
OL,12,Fto get him treatment.
OL,14,FParker himself called 999, telling the
OL,15,Fcall handler: "There is a woman who
OL,16,Fhas been badly injured."
OL,18,FPolice and paramedics found his mother
OL,19,Fin the hallway with a stab wound to
OL,20,Fher chest.
OL,26,@wD@OOU
