OL,3,CMan detained in hospital for killing
OL,4,Cmum in 'senseless' attack
OL,6,FAs well as murder, Parker was charged
OL,7,Fwith assault after headbutting and
OL,8,Fpunching his step-father in a previous
OL,9,Fattack.
